# EtherCAT PDOs -> cia402 (feedback/state)
net z-statusword       lcec.0.servo-z.status-word     => cia402.2.statusword
net z-opmode-display   lcec.0.servo-z.mode-display    => cia402.2.opmode-display
net z-drv-act-pos      lcec.0.servo-z.actual-position => cia402.2.drv-actual-position
net z-drv-act-vel      lcec.0.servo-z.actual-velocity => cia402.2.drv-actual-velocity

